name: Hey Mr. DJ
description: This is part of a live photography series titled "Music in Motion" which features several talented musicians I’ve had the privilege of photographing. The focal point of the imagery mirrors music itself by attempting to evoke emotions from the viewer. In order to maintain focus of the images these are sold in anonymity of the artists pictured. If you are interested in the musician's name I can denote it in the back of the print at time of shipping. To view more of my live photography visit our Live Galería.
